text: The Sierra Nevada National Park (Spanish: Parque Nacional Sierra Nevada) is a national park in Spain. It is in the Granada and Almería provinces. Its area is .Junta de Andalucía website Sierra Nevada was one of 100 finalists for the 12 Treasures of Spain in 2007. ==Geography== There are more than 20 peaks over .
